sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Geopolitical Analyst
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant Agent as Agentic Reasoning Engine
    participant KG as Neo4j (Graph)
    participant Vector as ZVec (Vector DB)
    participant LLM as Mistral Large

    User->>API: Submit Complex Query
    API->>Agent: Initialize Agentic Reasoning
    Agent->>LLM: Generate Search Plan (Decomposition)
    LLM-->>Agent: Plan: [Search Entities, Traverse Hops, Find Chunks]
    
    par Knowledge Retrieval
        Agent->>KG: Execute Multi-hop Traversal (Cypher)
        KG-->>Agent: Relational Triples
    and Semantic Retrieval
        Agent->>Vector: Semantic Similarity Search
        Vector-->>Agent: Contextual Text Chunks
    end

    Agent->>LLM: Preliminary Synthesis & Audit
    Note over Agent: Audit: Is the evidence sufficient?
    LLM-->>Agent: Refined Search Required (e.g., temporal check)
    Agent->>KG: Targeted Temporal Traversal
    KG-->>Agent: Final Evidence

    Agent->>LLM: Final Answer Generation (with Citations)
    LLM-->>Agent: Grounded Narrative
    Agent-->>API: Response + Reasoning Trace
    API-->>User: Visual Answer + Interactive Graph
